  "body": "### Description\r\nWith the introduction of [discovery options in the genesis file](https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/pull/2944), most of the constants in `org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.p2p.config.DiscoveryConfiguration` can be moved into its corresponding genesis file.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\nResolve the genesis content file early in the `org.hyperledger.besu.cli.BesuCommand` based on the `--network` option and then continue execution in the same way than with an external genesis file.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nThe `networkId` will still be hardcoded for each predefined network, but that can be addressed in a future pull request.\r\n",
